Class SearchForLocationActionContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.team23.weather.gui.SearchForLocationActionContext

  •  class SearchForLocationActionContext
extends java.lang.Object
    A SearchForLocationActionContext is an object containing all the user's input from the SearchForLocationPanel.

    Andrew Bloch-Hansen
    See Also:
